question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Hvor ligger Gyeongju Rådhus i Gyeongju, Sydkorea?
answer: Gyeongju Rådhus ligger i Hwangnam-dong, sentralt i Gyeongju, Sydkorea.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located in Hwangnam-dong, in the centre of Gyeongju, South Korea.
